      <p>Sometimes it‚Äôs useful to think that everyone else is an idiot. This lets you do things that no one else is doing. It‚Äôs best not to be too vocal about that. You can say something like ‚ÄúOh, I just thought I‚Äôd try out this direction‚Äù</p>
    </blockquote>
  </li>
